{"tid":565344,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"封利是竟然得十蚊!!?","createTime":"2018-02-19T01:12:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-19T01:12:03.000Z","uid":86545,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0c2e3548cafbe7c95d055e2bbe3938db08d6486e","tid":565344,"uid":86545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T01:12:03.000Z","msg":"雖然今年有四日假, 不過因為親戚太多 <br />\n所以年初三赤口都繼續拜年。<br />\n<br />\n話說昨日去了呀爸果邊的親戚屋企團拜, 計埋小朋友有成20幾人, 好熱鬧...<br />\n好多都係幾歲的小朋友。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n當長輩們都派緊利是的時候, 其中一個約十歲的小堂弟竟然玩即場拆利是<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n表弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 媽媽 你睇下 你睇下 ,有十蚊呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有十蚊呀~ 媽媽 竟然仲有人派十蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢媽媽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 唔好咁多野講 收返埋啦。<br />\n<br />\n之後我好好奇邊個親戚咁低賤?<br />\n<br />\n2018年都仲封10蚊??<br />\n<br />\n屌...原來係我大佬封的....<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呀哥立即影帝上身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n順手在個褲袋拎過第二封出來派比d 細路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :唔好意思,比錯果封平時用來比保安同埋茶樓職員。 呢封先係真, 學業進步呀 ～明仔<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另一方面, 老豆塊面黑到想唔認佢呢個仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}